OL,3,CGovernment sets target for 14,000
OL,4,Cprison cell spaces by 2031
OL,6,FThe Government has said it will build
OL,7,Ffour new prisons within the next seven
OL,8,Fyears in a bid to grip the
OL,9,Fovercrowding crisis.
OL,11,FThe Ministry of Justice (MoJ) promised
OL,12,Fto find a total of 14,000 cell spaces
OL,13,Fin jails by 2031.
OL,15,FSome 6,400 of these will be at newly
OL,16,Fbuilt prisons, with #2.3 billion
OL,17,Ftowards the cost over the next two
OL,18,Fyears.
