OL,6,FThe announcement comes after
OL,7,Fgovernment estimates published last
OL,8,Fweek indicated more than 100,000
OL,9,Fprisoners could be held in jails in
OL,10,FEngland and Wales by 2029.
OL,12,FThis followed warnings from
OL,13,FWhitehall's spending watchdog that
OL,14,FGovernment plans to boost prison
OL,15,Fcapacity could fall short by thousands
OL,16,Fof cell spaces within two years, and
OL,17,Fcost the taxpayer billions of pounds
OL,18,Fmore than anticipated.
